OL,3,CSex offender jailed after using secret
OL,4,Cphone to groom child
OL,6,FA sex offender from Maidstone has been
OL,7,Fsentenced to prison after breaching a
OL,8,FSexual Harm Prevention Order (SPHO)
OL,9,Fand secretly used a mobile phone in an
OL,10,Fattempt to groom a 13-year-old girl.
OL,12,FSean Royle had previously received a
OL,13,Fsuspended sentence in 2021, following
OL,14,Fconvictions which included the
OL,15,Fpossession of indecent images of
OL,16,Fchildren.
OL,18,FKent Police say the sentence included
OL,19,Fa SHPO, which contained a number of
OL,20,Fstrict measures and restrictions
OL,21,Fconcerning his access to the internet.
