OL,6,FHe had to notify police of any devices
OL,7,Fhe was using such as phones and
OL,8,Flaptops.
OL,10,FThe measures included requirements for
OL,11,FRoyle to notify police of any change
OL,12,Fin circumstances, such as a new
OL,13,Faddress or if he had any contact with
OL,14,Fchildren.
OL,16,FIn July 2023, checks established Royle
OL,17,Fwas in a relationship with a woman
OL,18,Fwith young children, but he had not
OL,19,Fdisclosed this to Kent Police and was
OL,20,Farrested.
