OL,6,FAn investigation led to the
OL,7,Fidentification of a phone number
OL,8,Flinked to him, which police say was
OL,9,Fbeing used secretly to access social
OL,10,Fmedia accounts.
OL,12,FOne of these accounts was a Snapchat
OL,13,Fprofile, which on 1 September was used
OL,14,Fby Royle to contact a child living
OL,15,Foutside of Kent.
OL,17,FKent Police say he established the
OL,18,Fvictim was 13, and after revealing he
OL,19,Fwas almost three times her age, told
OL,20,Fher he wanted to 'kiss and hug her.'
