OL,4,Cphone to groom child
OL,6,FRoyle, of Claremont Road, Maidstone
OL,7,Fasked her to be his girlfriend and
OL,8,Fsent a picture to the child showing
OL,9,Fhis face and naked upper torso which
OL,10,Fhad a distinctive tattoo - the victim
OL,11,Ftold her father who contacted the
OL,12,Fpolice.
OL,14,FHe was arrested again on 29 November
OL,15,F2023, when officers were able to
OL,16,Flocate and seize the phone he had been
OL,17,Fusing to contact the child.
OL,19,FWhen the device was analysed it was
OL,20,Ffound to contain almost 200 illegal
OL,21,Fvideos and images.
