OL,6,FThe 37-year-old was charged with
OL,7,Fmultiple offences, including engaging
OL,8,Fin sexual communication with a child,
OL,9,Ffailing to comply with notification
OL,10,Frequirements, repeated breaches of a
OL,11,Fsexual harm prevention order, and
OL,12,Fmaking indecent images of children.
OL,14,FRoyle pleaded guilty and on Thursday
OL,15,F21 November 2024, was sentenced to
OL,16,Fthree years and eight months, and was
OL,17,Fsubjected to a new ten-year SHPO.
