OL,6,F"When we seized his phone, it was also
OL,7,Fclear Royle had been was accessing
OL,8,Fmaterial which showed some of the
OL,9,Fworst offences against children
OL,10,Fimaginable, with many young victims
OL,11,Fsuffering appalling abuse.
OL,13,F"Sexual harm prevention orders such as
OL,14,Fthese are passed by the courts to help
OL,15,Fprotect children from harm and as this
OL,16,Fcase shows, we will do everything we
OL,17,Fcan to ensure those who ignore them
OL,18,Fface the consequences of their
OL,19,Factions."
